# Styling & Design System

- **Theme Tokens:** Strict prohibition of arbitrary values (e.g., `w-[312px]`). Use standard Tailwind scale from @tailwind.config.js.
- **Mobile-First:** Write base classes for mobile and use prefixes (`md:`, `lg:`) for larger screens.
- **Consistency:** Ensure colors and spacing match the shadcn/ui theme defined in global CSS.
- **A11y:** - Images must have descriptive `alt` tags. 
    - Icon-only buttons/links must have `aria-label`.
    - Maintain proper heading hierarchy (h1 -> h2 -> h3).